Descriptions

kz_chk_cruel
Original map by chorykapitan, KZMOD remake by Hardcore
Contains 1 course: kz_chk_cruel

kz_chk_cruel_h
Hard version of kz_chk_cruel

kz_grasshop
Original map author unknown
Contains 1 course: kz_grasshop

kz_mnk_dark
Original map by menko
Contains 1 course: kz_mnk_dark

kz_morath
Original map by Spider1, KZMOD port by Hardcore
Contains 2 courses: kz_morath and bhop_venice

kz_sunlight
Original map by Soft Serve, kz version by Hardcore and Menko
Contains 5 courses: kz_sunlight, kz_dragon_memorium, kz_prison, one unnamed secret course and a double duck course.

kz_wetbricks
Original map by Random Eye
Contains 2 courses: kz_wetbricks and bhop_resevoir

bkz_cubebhop
Original map by mls, KZMOD remake by Froupa
Contains 1 course: bkz_cubebhop

kz_bhop_canal_strafe
Original map by 007 and FragGyver
Contains 1 course: kz_bhop_canal_strafe
